Package fi.tamk.mindpuzzle

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidLauncher  
    AnswerScreen
    AnswerScreen shows the game's answer view after the QuestionScreen.
    CreditsScreen
    CreditsScreen shows team roles of the game's authors.
    FoodRoom
    FoodRoom shows the game's kitchen-themed room
    GameInstructionsScreen
    GameInstructionsScreen shows the game's instructions.
    HobbiesRoom
    HobbiesRoom shows the game's hobby-themed room
    LoadingScreen
    LoadingScreen loads all the assets to the game.
    MainMenuScreen
    MainMenuScreen is the main menu of the game including buttons for play, how to play, settings, credits and exit.
    MindPuzzle
    MindPuzzle is the main class of the application that contains metadata of the game and methods the game is operated with.
    PartyScreen
    PartyScreen is the ending screen or the game.
    QuestionScreen
    QuestionScreen shows the view for the character's multiple choice question.
    RoomMenuScreen
    RoomMenuScreen is the second menu of the game including menu button to return to the main menu and rooms sleep, food, social, hobbies and sports.
    SettingsPopUp
    SettingsPopUp is the settings view that opens from the rooms.
    SettingsScreen
    SettingsScreen is the settings view that opens from the main menu.
    SleepRoom
    SleepRoom shows the game's bedroom-themed room
    SocialRoom
    SocialRoom shows the game's living room-themed room
    SportsRoom
    SportsRoom shows the game's sport-themed backyard.
